---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="FAQ | Space Solutions"
  description="Frequently asked questions about interior design services from Space Solutions in Karnataka."
  headerScrolled={true}
>
  <PageHero
    breadcrumb={'<a href="/" style="color:inherit">Home</a> / FAQ'}
    title="FAQ"
  />

  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title fade-up" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-list fade-up">
        <div class="faq-item open">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            What interior design services does Space Solution offer in Karnataka?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Space Solution provides comprehensive interior design services across Karnataka, including home interior design, commercial interior design, and institutional interior design. Our expert team specializes in space planning, furniture selection, turnkey solutions, and custom design for residential, commercial, and institutional spaces.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            How does the interior design process work at Space Solution?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Our interior design process involves an initial consultation to understand your needs, followed by concept development, space planning, material selection, and execution. We ensure transparent communication and regular updates throughout your home, commercial, or institutional interior design project.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            Can Space Solution customize interior design solutions for my home or business?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, we offer personalized interior design solutions tailored to your style, requirements, and budget. Whether you need modern home interiors, functional office spaces, or innovative institutional designs, our team delivers bespoke results for every client.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            What is the cost of hiring an interior designer in Karnataka?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Interior design costs vary depending on the size of the project, the type of space (home, commercial, or institutional), materials chosen, and the scope of work. We provide detailed estimates after understanding your requirements and offer competitive pricing for all interior design services in Karnataka.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            What makes Space Solution different from other interior design companies in Karnataka?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Our interior design company stands out for its client-centric approach, innovative designs, attention to detail, and commitment to quality. We blend creativity with functionality to deliver interiors that reflect your vision and enhance your lifestyle or business environment.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            How long does an interior design project take to complete?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">The timeline for completing an interior design project depends on the complexity and scale of the work. Typically, residential and commercial interior design projects can range from a few weeks to a few months. We provide a clear project schedule and strive to meet all agreed deadlines.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            Does Space Solution handle turnkey interior design projects?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Absolutely. We offer turnkey interior design solutions, managing every aspect from concept and design to execution and final handover. This ensures a hassle-free experience for clients seeking home, commercial, or institutional interiors in Karnataka.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            Can I see samples of your previous interior design projects?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Yes, you can explore our portfolio showcasing a wide range of completed home interiors, commercial spaces, and institutional projects across Karnataka. Please visit our <a href="/portfolio">portfolio page</a> to view our work and get inspired for your own space.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            Do you offer interior design services outside major cities in Karnataka?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Space Solution provides interior design services throughout Karnataka, not just in major cities. We are committed to delivering high-quality interior solutions to clients in urban and rural locations across the state.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" type="button">
            How do I get started with Space Solution for my interior design project?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Getting started is easy! <a href="/contact">Contact us</a> through our website or call our team to schedule an initial consultation. We will discuss your requirements, provide expert guidance, and help you begin your journey toward beautiful and functional interiors in Karnataka.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
